{"tid":1799102,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"2007 Stepwgn 電窗卡住卡住","createTime":"2019-12-26T16:50:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-27T04:03:52.000Z","uid":317731,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8da27ac81f099a5fc5bb715647ec84e3ad6aa09a","tid":1799102,"uid":317731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T16:50:49.000Z","msg":"是咁的...<br />\n2007 Stepwgn <br />\n約一個半月前, 部Stepwgn 司機位電窗卡住卡住，做唔到一下auto 上或者落。如是者大約兩星期後，部車打埋柴撻唔著，自己去換電，但換電後，隻窗又回復正常可以按一下就自動上或者落。<br />\n<br />\n一個月後，隻窗既問題又返黎，想問問有冇人知係咩問題？會唔會係死左打爛磨？因為理論上舊電換左一個月，望過仍係綠色，咁應該仲有電。<br />\n<br />\nAnyway, 都已諗住聽日揸出去比車房睇下。"},{"pid":"a22d90a5a3cd894b1f6f6366f7fff112200a5093","tid":1799102,"uid":76213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T17:51:55.000Z","msg":"wd40"},{"pid":"f40e3b29f2d680e80f82856ca0be08c4620e91f4","tid":1799102,"uid":23897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a22d90a5a3cd894b1f6f6366f7fff112200a5093","tid":1799102,"uid":76213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T17:51:55.000Z","msg":"wd40"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T03:40:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UR5XD2W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUR5XD2W.jpg&h=19425b36&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dab6d87fb2cb34509df7130de6240f6e95ef7dcf","tid":1799102,"uid":317731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T04:03:52.000Z","msg":"最後琴日甩左負極接電成晚，今朝先去接返，結果係成功了！隻窗回復正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但好想知係乜野原因"}]}